  "title": "💫Events and Marketing (Travel Opportunities)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>Royal Org is one of the newest and fastest growing outsourced sales and marketing firms specializing in face-to-face marketing and revenue generation. Our committed team enhances clients’ branding and reputation by engaging thousands of people daily about their vision and products.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will support and introduce new customers to our clients by building relationships and driving new business in a fast-paced, high-growth environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Engage potential customers through clear and persuasive communication to introduce clients’ products and services</li><li>Build and maintain positive relationships with prospects to increase client customer base</li><li>Demonstrate persistence by following up on leads and turning initial rejections into sales opportunities</li><li>Collaborate with team members to meet realistic sales goals and contribute to overall team success</li><li>Participate actively in coaching sessions to develop sales skills and improve performance</li><li>Attend regular team and company social events to foster a supportive and collaborative work culture</li></ul>",
